data.description: You will LOVE the Lake Murray views from your large, screened deck on this mountain cabin styled home in Marina Cove. Lake living under $300,000!  HVAC updated in 2021. Located on beautiful Lake Murray, the community has a pool, playground, dock,  boat ramp and gazebos included with home ownership.  Multifunction lower level can be used as a spacious master bedroom or additional space to entertain.  Roomy screened in 2nd level deck overlooking the water is perfect for outside dining relaxing or spending time with friends. High ceilings and beautiful wood finish give you a mountain cabin feel with a water view. Gated storage area in back of subdivision available for boat/camper/trailer parking with additional overflow parking near the pool. HVAC updated in 2021 with a new Trane 2.5 ton Heat Pump. Seller to leave freestanding corner electric fireplace and wall mounted TV in 2nd floor living area. Mounted cabinet (top and bottom) in 2nd floor living area to remain. Make your move to Lake Living now!
